lines.text: Pursuant to the offer of Global Depository Receipts (GDRs) made by the Company in 1993,
5,56,13,501 GDRs, representing 5,56,13,501 underlying Shares of the Company i.e. 1.48% of the
issued and subscribed Share Capital, were outstanding as on 31st March, 2007.
The Company's GDRs are listed on the Luxembourg Stock Exchange (Code: 004660919) at Societe
de la Bourse de Luxembourg, 11, av de la Porte-Neuve, L-2227 Luxembourg. The Listing Fee for the
